# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# REQUIRED IN PRODUCTION - Server will fail to start in production without this
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------

# Frontend URL (REQUIRED in production mode)
# This is used for CORS configuration - only this origin will be allowed
# Example: https://yourdomain.com
# In development, defaults to http://localhost:3000
